# Nest.js Patterns

- Modules: `*Module` di root folder fitur
- Controllers: `@Controller('route')` — delegasikan ke service
- Services: business logic, inject repository dengan `@InjectRepository`
- DTOs: class-validator decorators, `@ApiProperty` untuk Swagger
- Entities: TypeORM decorators, `@DeleteDateColumn` untuk soft delete
- Error: `NotFoundException`, `UnprocessableEntityException`, `BadRequestException`
- Response: `{ data }`, `{ data, meta }`, `{ error: { code, message } }`
- Refer ke `../todo-shared-ai-native-orchestration/architecture/api-contracts.md` untuk kontrak
